name: kelly ford
text: Best Customer Service. They specially made me an AWESOME TACO PIZZA and specially wrapped it for my long drive home. They were so nice and helpful. You earned my loyalty for me and my family. We love Friday night pizza nights in our home and now we consider you part of our family's favorite ! Thank you Papa Murphy's Dublin Team !

name: Levintry
text: I have been visiting this particular location for over a year now and the best way to describe is it outstanding consistency. The inside and outside of the store are always very clean showing a true sense of ownership by the staff. The …More

name: The Traveling Rose
text: Love this place! The food is amazing and so fresh, the workers are always so kind and easy going. My only complaint is that it's a little pricey considering they don't use energy to cook the pizza, since you cook it yourself.

name: Lindsey Carole
text:
Some of my favorite pizza.  Love the deals.

Edit- absolutley heartbroken this location is closing!! Such great service and great food. Hope the other locations are good

name: Mike Murphy
text: Excellent food... even better service. This store has great employees.

name: Roxanne Euber
text: OMG, how did I not discover this place sooner?? Super fast, friendly, and very clean. They have tons of toppings and crazy coupon deals too. My new pizza place.

name: Trevor O'Dell
text: Very friendly. Allowed me to customize a menu item to suit dietary needs without any additional charge, then held the pizza for us while we went shopping for more exotic ingredients to add later.

name: Denise Willey
text: Great manager Allen and good staff. They treat me well there. Always have made my orders great.

name: Dianne Walck
text: Delicious pizza and salad and even dessert!   Love taking pizza home to bake and serving hot from the oven!   Coupons are often confusing and difficult to use.    If this problem was fixed, I'd give them 5 stars!

name: J.P. Purswell
text: This location takes longer to get to than my "regular" Papa Murphy's (at Briargate Pkwy and Union), but it is open an hour later. The pizza tastes the same (as I would expect).  I've stopped by here on my way home from my walks at Blodgett Peak Open Space.

name: Daniel H.
text: Pizza was good, staff seemed rushed and confused, manager wasn't helping the staff at all. 1 more try

name: Robert Boule
text: Good price, great selection, fast service

name: Elizabeth Behnke
text: This Papa Murpheys location always has outstanding service! The people are friendly and they are really fast! I have called them while I am on my way to the store location and they have my pizza ready by the time I get there. Superb! If you don't like other Papa Murpheys locations, come to this one!

name: Pamela Hamilton
text: 4 times in a row! I know how stupid of me to keep giving them another chance.  Last time I ordered, in person, pepperoni and 1/2 pepper ,meaning on 1 side only and I told the asshat that 3x 1 side only and what did I get SAUSAGE and pepper …More

name: Phoebe Bengogullari
text: I love their thin crust pizza!! It is absolutely delicious!

name: Trauma Llama
text: In and out fast, about all I want with a food place.

name: Heather East
text: Stopped in tonight because I had not tried papa murphy's before.  I got a basic pepperoni pizza.  Tasted and smelled like plastic.  I paid 5$ and did not get my money's worth.

name: Cindy Pogue
text: Great staff, very friendly. Good pizza!

name: Mike Nutz
text: My daughter has to have a gluten free diet and they were very accommodating to this.

name: Andrew Parker
text: Best location.  The only one I go to even with one much closer to my neighborhood.

name: Jeff Wiese
text:
This trip the pizza was bland.
Not their best quality this trip.

name: Shane Swansin
text: Love this spot quick easy friendly.  So no more fam.

name: Justin Bailey
text: Great pizza but the service was slow and staff messed up the order and did so for several people.

name: Dave Cunningham
text: This store is always very fast and friendly. They never skimp on their pizza ingredients. A very professional environment that keeps us coming back.

name: Matthew Williams
text: Never disappointed, the pizza here is great and service is very quick

name: Jennifer D. Svihl
text: Fast, friendly service. Pizza is always delicious.

name: Eugene Armstead, Jr.
text: Great pizza. Great crew. Great attitudes.

name: John Ward
text: Good pizza at a good price. Sign up for their text deals for extra savings.

name: Elyssa Weber
text: Awesome but the stuffed pizza gets soggy fast

name: Reggie Barrau
text: I didn't walk in, but the food was excellent!

name: Jonathan Fisher
text: It's closed.

name: Paul Koch
text: This location CLOSED.

name: Jillian D
text: Good, fast service.

name: xiaoyi Drake
text: Great service

name: Tierriney Strickland
text: Got gas

name: Yashica Scott
text: The best pizza... Hands down...

name: Mike Conner
text: Love love it
